Reality Tv star Nina has replied Nigerians living abroad discouraging others willing to relocate from doing so. NIna was among the top five of the season three Big Brother Nigeria. She said it was nonsensical to use one’s experience to discourage those willing to give relocation a try.   Six celebrities who became parents by surrogacy     Nigerian-American rapper, King Joel rewards school with…     Ex-BBNaija’s Angel applauds self for accomplishments…   She said in her Instastory: “I don’t understand why people abroad would be trying so hard to make it looks like it’s a struggle living there here and then trying to discourage other people from relocating if life is that hard here or you don’t like the snow so much or all the taxes you pay out here. - Advertisement - “Brooo go back to your country and let others come. Abeg make we hear word enough of all that nonsense.” The Reality TV star is based in the United States of America with her husband and son.